 Affair","video":false,"overview":"The only thing worse than being the assistant to a high-maintenance movie star who doesn't take you seriously? Finding out he's smitten with your mom.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7544,"vote_count":700,"poster_path":"/l0CaVyqnTsWwNd4hWsrLNEk1Wjd.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-27","vote_average":5.739,"backdrop_path":"/ngLxW9WqQAkTCBTcjOSt2Pnz5qZ.jpg","original_title":"A Family Affair","original_language":"en"},{"id":746036,"adult":false,"title":"The Fall Guy","video":false,"overview":"Fresh off an almost career-ending accident, stuntman Colt Seavers has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job.","genre_ids":[28,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.1778,"vote_count":3523,"poster_path":"/e7olqFmzcIX5c23kX4zSmLPJi8c.jpg","release_date":"2024-04-24","vote_average":6.958,"backdrop_path":"/H5HjE7Xb9N09rbWn1zBfxgI8uz.jpg","original_title":"The Fall Guy","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":35,"adult":false,"title":"The Simpsons Movie","video":false,"overview":"After Homer accidentally pollutes the town's water supply, Springfield is encased in a gigantic dome by the EPA and the Simpsons are declared fugitives.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"popularity":7.6436,"vote_count":8433,"poster_path":"/s3b8TZWwmkYc2KoJ5zk77qB6PzY.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-25","vote_average":7.019,"backdrop_path":"/8ln5VUVk7gnNGIb2VNgw8nICDVt.jpg","original_title":"The Simpsons Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":58,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","video":false,"overview":"Jack's got a blood debt to pay: he owes his soul to the legendary Davy Jones, ghastly Ruler of the Ocean Depths.  But ever-crafty Jack isn't about to go down without a fight.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":13.4319,"vote_count":16906,"poster_path":"/uXEqmloGyP7UXAiphJUu2v2pcuE.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-06","vote_average":7.374,"backdrop_path":"/vr6n6ZFUZvedvIlhfYcbCWcaKyW.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest","original_language":"en"},{"id":71,"adult":false,"title":"Billy Elliot","video":false,"overview":"County Durham, England, 1984. The miners' strike has started and the police have started coming up from Bethnal Green, starting a class war with the lower classes suffering. Caught in the middle of the conflict is 11-year old Billy Elliot, who, after leaving his boxing club for the day, stumbles upon a ballet class and finds out that he's naturally talented. He practices with his teacher Mrs. Wilkinson for an upcoming audition in Newcastle-upon Tyne for the royal Ballet school in London.","genre_ids":[18,35,10402],"popularity":2.8329,"vote_count":4027,"poster_path":"/nOr5diUZxphmAD3li9aiILyI28F.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-28","vote_average":7.593,"backdrop_path":"/mTsbahr4SLqgVZkKRN0O8t5iA9y.jpg","original_title":"Billy Elliot","original_language":"en"},{"id":95,"adult":false,"title":"Armageddon","video":false,"overview":"When an asteroid threatens to collide with Earth, NASA honcho Dan Truman determines the only way to stop it is to drill into its surface and detonate a nuclear bomb. This leads him to renowned driller Harry Stamper, who agrees to helm the dangerous space mission provided he can bring along his own hotshot crew. Among them is the cocksure A.J. who Harry thinks isn't good enough for his daughter, until the mission proves otherwise.","genre_ids":[28,53,878,12],"popularity":8.4133,"vote_count":8425,"poster_path":"/eTM3qtGhDU8cvjpoa6KEt5E2auU.jpg","release_date":"1998-07-01","vote_average":6.829,"backdrop_path":"/1cO6OQJxz7YhTZ4V1OlkYfebeJa.jpg","original_title":"Armageddon","original_language":"en"},{"id":96,"adult":false,"title":"Beverly Hills Cop II","video":false,"overview":"Axel Foley returns to the land of sunshine and palm trees to investigate the near-fatal shooting of police Captain Andrew Bogomil. With the help of Sgt. Taggart and Det. Rosewood, they soon uncover that the shooting is associated with a series of \"alphabet\" robberies masterminded by a heartless weapons kingpin—and the chase is on.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":4.3923,"vote_count":2756,"poster_path":"/egDakU8O5yUwpUJP9IMAUVtIDll.jpg","release_date":"1987-05-18","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/bIA65PCRtIQfBvIoKohJbtOPl3M.jpg","original_title":"Beverly Hills Cop II","original_language":"en"},{"id":100,"adult":false,"title":"Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels","video":false,"overview":"A card shark and his unwillingly-enlisted friends need to make a lot of cash quick after losing a sketchy poker match. To do this they decide to pull a heist on a small-time gang who happen to be operating out of the flat next door.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":2.87,"vote_count":7056,"poster_path":"/6pJB2t3MbQUy9m5pFIBHXLqnqNd.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-28","vote_average":8.098,"backdrop_path":"/cXQH2u7wUIX1eoIdEj51kHXoWhX.jpg","original_title":"Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels","original_language":"en"},{"id":153,"adult":false,"title":"Lost in Translation","video":false,"overview":"Two lost souls visiting Tokyo -- the young, neglected wife of a photographer and a washed-up movie star shooting a TV commercial -- find an odd solace and pensive freedom to be real in each other's company, away from their lives in America.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"popularity":5.9969,"vote_count":7908,"poster_path":"/3jCLmYDIIiSMPujbwygNpqdpM8N.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-18","vote_average":7.383,"backdrop_path":"/6ITVHoipvxAS8luzKtHTbPaHLtT.jpg","original_title":"Lost in Translation","original_language":"en"},{"id":204,"adult":false,"title":"The Wages of Fear","video":false,"overview":"In a run-down South American town, four men are paid to drive trucks loaded with nitroglycerin into the jungle through to the oil field. Friendships are tested and rivalries develop as they embark upon the perilous journey.","genre_ids":[18,53,12],"popularity":1.9299,"vote_count":1053,"poster_path":"/sNOvIp4X0fmCMfgEs2ww5IyMgFm.jpg","release_date":"1953-04-22","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/hTP6H7sNlWXdGxAciXQSjNJ1ob7.jpg","original_title":"Le Salaire de la peur","original_language":"fr"},{"id":243,"adult":false,"title":"High Fidelity","video":false,"overview":"After his long-time girlfriend dumps him, a thirty-year-old record store owner seeks to understand why he is unlucky in love while recounting his \"top five breakups of all time\".","genre_ids":[18,35,10749,10402],"popularity":4.0749,"vote_count":2143,"poster_path":"/e2LZGB62GMhv3Fo8tDZjY87I81a.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-17","vote_average":7.13,"backdrop_path":"/tmP4COlAaowO0FniW30aatOcmMq.jpg","original_title":"High Fidelity","original_language":"en"},{"id":253,"adult":false,"title":"Live and Let Die","video":false,"overview":"James Bond must investigate a mysterious murder case of a British agent in New Orleans. Soon he finds himself up against a gangster boss named Mr. Big.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":3.8501,"vote_count":2226,"poster_path":"/39qkrjqMZs6utwNmihVImC3ghas.jpg","release_date":"1973-06-27","vote_average":6.509,"backdrop_path":"/hzmmXx6UeYQeylioNbliFKjSbV7.jpg","original_title":"Live and Let Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":114,"adult":false,"title":"Pretty Woman","video":false,"overview":"While on a business trip in Los Angeles, Edward Lewis, a millionaire entrepreneur who makes a living buying and breaking up companies, picks up a prostitute, Vivian, while asking for directions; after, Edward hires Vivian to stay with him for the weekend to accompany him to a few social events, and the two get closer only to discover there are significant hurdles to overcome as they try to bridge the gap between their very different worlds.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":9.2826,"vote_count":8845,"poster_path":"/hVHUfT801LQATGd26VPzhorIYza.jpg","release_date":"1990-03-23","vote_average":7.455,"backdrop_path":"/sGEqHTylawwS6hwKultk1mKUjdB.jpg","original_title":"Pretty Woman","original_language":"en"},{"id":121,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","video":false,"overview":"Frodo Baggins and the other members of the Fellowship continue on their sacred quest to destroy the One Ring--but on separate paths. Their destinies lie at two towers--Orthanc Tower in Isengard, where the corrupt wizard Saruman awaits, and Sauron's fortress at Barad-dur, deep within the dark lands of Mordor. Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":17.7989,"vote_count":23478,"poster_path":"/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-18","vote_average":8.413,"backdrop_path":"/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","original_language":"en"},{"id":122,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","video":false,"overview":"As armies mass for a final battle that will decide the fate of the world--and powerful, ancient forces of Light and Dark compete to determine the outcome--one member of the Fellowship of the Ring is revealed as the noble heir to the throne of the Kings of Men. Yet, the sole hope for triumph over evil lies with a brave hobbit, Frodo, who, accompanied by his loyal friend Sam and the hideous, wretched Gollum, ventures deep into the very dark heart of Mordor on his seemingly impossible quest to destroy the Ring of Power.​","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":23.6525,"vote_count":26078,"poster_path":"/rCzpDGLbOoPwLjy3OAm5NUPOTrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-17","vote_average":8.494,"backdrop_path":"/2u7zbn8EudG6kLlBzUYqP8RyFU4.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","original_language":"en"},{"id":284,"adult":false,"title":"The Apartment","video":false,"overview":"Bud Baxter is a minor clerk in a huge New York insurance company, until he discovers a quick way to climb the corporate ladder. He lends out his apartment to the executives as a place to take their mistresses. Although he often has to deal with the aftermath of their visits, one night he's left with a major problem to solve.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":4.7929,"vote_count":2580,"poster_path":"/hhSRt1KKfRT0yEhEtRW3qp31JFU.jpg","release_date":"1960-06-21","vote_average":8.19,"backdrop_path":"/2L8U8rUyWeFTb6n1egTNeJsEsvj.jpg","original_title":"The Apartment","original_language":"en"},{"id":285,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End","video":false,"overview":"Captain Jack Sparrow is trapped in Davy Jones' Locker when his pirate brethren begin a desperate quest to locate and rescue him. Follow their wild seafaring adventures from exotic Singapore to World's End and beyond.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":12.849,"vote_count":15233,"poster_path":"/jGWpG4YhpQwVmjyHEGkxEkeRf0S.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-19","vote_average":7.267,"backdrop_path":"/1jHxkVXMI5s3vRiyiZooUy1shB5.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End","original_language":"en"},{"id":299,"adult":false,"title":"Ocean's Eleven","video":false,"overview":"Danny Ocean and his gang attempt to rob the five biggest casinos in Las Vegas in one night.","genre_ids":[80,35],"popularity":3.4481,"vote_count":388,"poster_path":"/A4R6u7SidBPVXMVzGSysCiRGTRz.jpg","release_date":"1960-08-10","vote_average":6.366,"backdrop_path":"/vJLSt7NvYP85nR4XJ8CxnMadf6G.jpg","original_title":"Ocean's Eleven","original_language":"en"},{"id":154,"adult":false,"title":"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","video":false,"overview":"The starship Enterprise and its crew is pulled back into action when old nemesis, Khan, steals a top secret device called Project Genesis.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,53],"popularity":3.5314,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/uPyLsKl8Z0LOoxeaFXsY5MxhR5s.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-04","vote_average":7.445,"backdrop_path":"/meqmvZjKpQ7WRhpZvIoKIAvioSD.jpg","original_title":"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","original_language":"en"},{"id":158,"adult":false,"title":"Knockin' on Heaven's Door","video":false,"overview":"Two young men, Martin and Rudi, both suffering from terminal cancer, get to know each other in a hospital room. They drown their desperation in tequila and decide to take one last trip to the sea. Drunk and still in pajamas they steal the first fancy car they find, a 60's Mercedes convertible. The car happens to belong to a bunch of gangsters, which immediately start to chase it, since it contains more than the pistol Martin finds in the glove box.","genre_ids":[35,80,28,18],"popularity":1.7437,"vote_count":571,"poster_path":"/dsY09zCxKDFjfV1oqXFJJpVrHdP.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-20","vote_average":7.687,"backdrop_path":"/yXnlw2SB0QhYUC4QDyuRZh3CQlU.jpg","original_title":"Knockin' on Heaven's Door","original_language":"de"},{"id":195,"adult":false,"title":"Trouble in Paradise","video":false,"overview":"Thief Gaston Monescu and pickpocket Lily are partners in crime and love. Working for perfume company executive Mariette Colet, the two crooks decide to combine their criminal talents to rob their employer. Under the alias of Monsieur Laval, Gaston uses his position as Mariette's personal secretary to become closer to her. However, he takes things too far when he actually falls in love with Mariette, and has to choose between her and Lily.","genre_ids":[35,80,10749],"popularity":0.6132,"vote_count":301,"poster_path":"/FBxuoLRD3Biyul14unT5m3PYNS.jpg","release_date":"1932-10-30","vote_average":7.41,"backdrop_path":"/8xFIubJoxyidKaGjO1dc0btC9e7.jpg","original_title":"Trouble in Paradise","original_language":"en"},{"id":654028,"adult":false,"title":"The Christmas Chronicles: Part Two","video":false,"overview":"Kate Pierce is reluctantly spending Christmas with her mom’s new boyfriend and h